{"tid":727134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"贏國「新時代號」佈滿習大大經典語句 員工領唱紅歌","createTime":"2018-07-02T21:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T02:11:50.000Z","uid":95520,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"d0c6b49bfa657c7dc8c38a0fcb7c6196c117c9be","tid":727134,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T21:42:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1771260823018396/?t=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1771260823018396%2F%3Ft%3D0&d=SuPqgqUjISO5dWD9iAOmRtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=684777db\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1771260823018396/?t=0</a><br />\n【長春地鐵「新時代號」】【乘客：很震撼、很有意義】<br />\n<br />\n登上「新時代號」，看著習近平一句句的經典語句，乘客有何感受呢？<br />\n<br />\n「這個形式我們很震撼」<br />\n<br />\n「希望祖國越來越繁榮昌盛」<br />\n<br />\n「黨的生日參加這活動我覺得很有意義」<br />\n<br />\n「新時代號」通車日，車上有宣講活動，月台更有員工領唱紅歌。<br />\n  #不忘初心 #新時代新列車<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/053949_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F053949_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=fec0a38f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/03/053611_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2F053611_c38fc3ba97e79d4dc14133597a0b7033.PNG&h=c0f2d9ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"feceb45c77cb2d1819d76564801c8ecd1ffbd3b3","tid":727134,"uid":66943,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T21:57:33.000Z","msg":"屌你邪教咁"},{"pid":"0444f89b8f332bb48ff459e9496076f23651ab73","tid":727134,"uid":173631,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T21:59:00.000Z","msg":"哇，屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hah